WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: the windows path — Tailscale MSI from the official download.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: the MSI bundles the WinTUN driver and the tailscale service.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: after install the tray icon prompts for a login server URL.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: paste the operator URL and the preauth key into the dialog.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: a UAC prompt confirms the WinTUN driver activation.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: tailscale status from PowerShell mirrors the linux output.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: ping a peer from cmd.exe — the data plane traverses normally.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:15.000
narrator: the windows host is now a member of the same tailnet.
